description:
This plugin is a drop in CSV Excel data importer for Bubble database. 

It allows developers to import customer CSV Excel data into Bubble database in a few minutes.
name: CSV Excel Importer | csvbox.io
plugin_instructions:
Instructions available here - https://help.csvbox.io/destinations/bubble.io


See demo app here - https://csvbox-demo.bubbleapps.io/version-test
